Articles.Content: I am using rescaled 0.5 PorkWorks parts to build and send a space station to Eve. This is the first of 8 KSO shuttle missions to construct and deploy the station.

The Twenty-Fourth of my STS KSO Shuttle Missions and Twentieth Flight of the Tenacious! STS 124's objective is to deploy the KSO Eve Space Station Science Bay Module and return to the KSC Runway!

The construction and deployment missions run STS 123 through STS 130.


Most of the footage is shown in 4x speed for quick viewing.

STS 125 will deploy the Eve Station Habitat Module #1! Edited March 10, 2014 by Westi29
